. The conspecifity of 
<taxonomicName id="C2BDE6FFFFC254332FA0F866FCC1F98D" box="[685,845,1553,1578]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angustulus">
