</taxonomicName>
is judged from the generally accepted concept of 
<taxonomicName id="C2BDE6FFFFC254332F5BF84EFD7AF9F5" box="[598,758,1593,1618]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="3" pageNumber="4" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="angustulus">
